  "page": "Eustace (Braavos)",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div role=\"note\" class=\"hatnote navigation-not-searchable\" style=\"font-style: italic;padding-left: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">For others with the same name, see <a href=\"/index.php/Eustace\" title=\"Eustace\">Eustace</a>.</div>\n<table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Faith_of_the_Seven\" title=\"Faith of the Seven\"><img alt=\"Star of the Faith.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/9/91/Star_of_the_Faith.svg/50px-Star_of_the_Faith.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/9/91/Star_of_the_Faith.svg/75px-Star_of_the_Faith.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/9/91/Star_of_the_Faith.svg/100px-Star_of_the_Faith.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Septon</span><br />Eustace</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Braavos\" title=\"Braavos\"><img alt=\"Braavos.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/a/a2/Braavos.svg/50px-Braavos.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/a/a2/Braavos.svg/75px-Braavos.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/a/a2/Braavos.svg/100px-Braavos.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\nSepton</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Faith_of_the_Seven\" title=\"Faith of the Seven\">Faith of the Seven</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Cultures</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Westeros\" title=\"Westeros\">Westerosi</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/Braavos\" title=\"Braavos\">Braavosi</a></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Eustace</b> is a disgraced and defrocked septon of the <a href=\"/index.php/Faith_of_the_Seven\" title=\"Faith of the Seven\">Faith of the Seven</a> who used to be attached to the <a href=\"/index.php/Sept-Beyond-the-Sea\" title=\"Sept-Beyond-the-Sea\">Sept-Beyond-the-Sea</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/Braavos\" title=\"Braavos\">Braavos</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Eustace_(Braavos)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Feast_for_Crows\"><i>A Feast for Crows</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Eustace_(Braavos)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Feast for Crows\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Eustace performs weddings at the <a href=\"/index.php/Happy_Port\" title=\"Happy Port\">Happy Port</a> for the <a href=\"/index.php/Sailor%27s_Wife\" title=\"Sailor&#39;s Wife\">Sailor's Wife</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>  \n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Eustace_(Braavos)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Raffc34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows-Chapter_34\" title=\"A Feast for Crows-Chapter 34\">Chapter 34</a>, Cat Of The Canals.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403172339\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.107 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.403 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 533/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 10485/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 5983/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 282/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 814/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.270/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 6.72 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  392.600      1 -total\n 88.34%  346.837      1 Template:Infobox_character\n 87.71%  344.331      1 Template:Infobox\n 12.22%   47.993     12 Template:Infobox_value\n  9.45%   37